+- [ ] CHK024 Are the assumptions about available course and instructor data validated by explicit fallback requirements when those dependencies are stale, incomplete, or temporarily unavailable? [Assumption, Dependency, Spec §Assumptions, Spec §Dependencies]
+- [ ] CHK025 Does the spec clearly separate guaranteed requirements from planning assumptions about future schedule-generation behavior? [Consistency, Assumption, Spec §Assumptions, Spec §Dependencies, Plan §Summary]
