+**Goal**: Let a student save a full valid term-scoped priority set and have schedule ranking use the latest saved values
+
+**Independent Test**: Open the priority editor for one term with eligible constraints, assign valid priorities from 1 to 5 to all eligible constraints, save, reload the term, and confirm later ranking reads the latest saved priority set
